{
  "stem": "5261.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was great help for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She never went to the market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She [? need'nt-- ?] she didn't-- she need-- she had not in the [? amount ?] to buy because I brought this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I received as a compensation for my [INAUDIBLE], for my work there in the garden or in the market with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was maybe very good opportunity because by this gardener, I learned a little German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And especially because my mother finished only German-- four classes German school-- my father, also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sometimes they wanted to say amongst them something secretly, and they spoke German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very angry that I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Therefore ?] I [? insistent ?] to learn so quickly, and there would be not so secrets for me because I-- I could speak a little also German.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our relation was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had not so big income, but everybody did something, and everybody tried to bring home-- even me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I received some sweets from my gardener or from this Jew lady, this owner of restaurant, I never-- never ate alone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I brought home, and my mother share it to everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father, also receive-- I never forget-- sometimes he receive some tips.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He brought some sprats, smoked sprats, a case of them-- she [? divide ?] so that we-- I have the best memory from my home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was educated from my mother in the honest way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said always, don't lie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who lies, [? steal. ?] And you must be honest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have the best experience, the best memories from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you see, it was only the tailor give us in very good-- very good rates for-- to pay for this uniform-- I don't know exactly, maybe one year.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
